  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/2377",
  "title": "fix: update call to refine",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThe signature of the `refine` method in `PriceRanges` has [recently changed](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/a5a691649bb7bd33bd0dc933ebbccf365bdc7e5c). But the `PriceRanges` instantiate an other component `PriceRangesForm` that also use the `refine` method as `prop`.\r\n\r\nThe call of `refine` inside `PriceRangesForm` hasn't be changed, and throw an error when we try to `preventDefault` on the event that is actually a number.\r\n\r\nYou can try the `PriceRanges` component [in the documentation](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/priceRanges.html), press `Go` and the component will throw an error.\r\n",
